@lap v0.3
# Machine-readable API spec. Each @endpoint block is one API call.
@api Randommer API
@version v1
@auth ApiKey X-Api-Key in header
@common_fields {X-Api-Key: str}
@endpoints 25
@hint download_for_search
@toc api(25)

